hite/10 rounded-sm p-4\" style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05),0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.18)\">\n            <p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold\" style=\"color: white\">Persönlicher Ansprechpartner</p>\n            <p class=\"mt-1 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed\" style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7)\">Vom ersten Gespräch bis zur Übergabe erreichbar und verantwortlich.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-4\" style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05),0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.18)\">\n            <p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold\" style=\"color: white\">Transparente Kosten</p>\n            <p class=\"mt-1 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed\" style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7)\">Klare Aufstellung, nachvollziehbare Entscheidungen und regelmäßige Reports.</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-4\" style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);box-shadow:inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05),0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.18)\">\n            <p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold\" style=\"color: white\">Regionale Expertise</p>\n            <p class=\"mt-1 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed\" style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7)\">Erfolgreiche Bauprojekte und echte Kundenstimmen aus Norddeutschland.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"relative\">\n        <div class=\"absolute -inset-6 rounded-[1.25rem] pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%,rgba(255,255,255,0.08),transparent 65%);filter:blur(18px)\"></div>\n        <div class=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm border border-white/10\" style=\"box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35),0 0 40px rgba(255,255,255,0.04)\">\n          <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/800/600?random=11\" alt=\"Baumanagement auf einer Baustelle in Norddeutschland mit persönlicher Projektbetreuung\" class=\"w-full h-[420px] md:h-[620px] object-cover\">\n          <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-black/15 to-transparent\"></div>\n          <div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.12),transparent 32%,transparent 68%,rgba(255,255,255,0.06));mix-blend-mode:screen\"></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"absolute left-4 right-4 -bottom-6 md:left-8 md:right-auto md:max-w-sm border border-white/10 rounded-sm p-5\" style=\"background:rgba(0,0,0,0.55);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.28),inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\">\n          <p class=\"text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed font-semibold\" style=\"color: white\">Wenn Bauprojekte aus dem Ruder laufen, fehlt meist nicht Einsatz — sondern Struktur.</p>\n          <ul class=\"mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed\" style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78)\">\n            <li>• Kosten und Zeit bleiben kontrollierbar</li>\n            <li>• Baufortschritt ist jederzeit nachvollziehbar</li>\n            <li>• Keine wechselnden Ansprechpartner</li>\n            <li>• Echte Referenzen statt schöner Versprechen</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
